OL,3,CThe private investigators who exposed
OL,4,CHorizon IT scandal
OL,6,FForensic accountants Ron Warmington
OL,7,Fand Ian Henderson exclusively tell ITV
OL,8,FNews Correspondent John Ray about the
OL,9,F"most difficult case" they have ever
OL,10,Fworked on
OL,12,FThey make unlikely heroes: Two men of
OL,13,Fa certain age dressed in dark blue
OL,14,Fsuits.
OL,16,FRon Warmington and Ian Henderson are
OL,17,Fnumber crunchers. Bean counters. And
OL,18,Fto hundreds of persecuted people,
OL,19,Fsaviours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
