OL,6,F"It's the most difficult case we've
OL,7,Fever worked on. But by miles the most
OL,8,Fimportant", Mr Warmington said.
OL,10,FBetween them, they have investigated
OL,11,Fmulti-million pound frauds and
OL,12,Fextortion rackets; even given expert
OL,13,Fevidence in the Wagatha Christie trial.
OL,15,FBut nothing compares to their
OL,16,Fexperience with the Post Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
