OL,6,F"It's when you meet the postmasters,"
OL,7,Fsaid Mr Henderson. "That's why you do
OL,8,Fit. They're the heart of the
OL,9,Fcommunity. And they were badly led
OL,10,Fdown by the Post Office."
OL,12,FMr Henderson and Mr Warmington
OL,13,Ftogether are Second Sight; the
OL,14,Fforensic accountants brought in `
OL,15,Freluctantly - by the Post Office more
OL,16,Fthan a decade ago to look for errors
OL,17,Fin their costly IT system, Horizon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
