OL,3,CThe private investigators who exposed
OL,4,CHorizon IT scandal
OL,6,FAhead of their appearance at the
OL,7,Fofficial inquiry on Tuesday, the two
OL,8,Fmen sat down for an exclusive joint
OL,9,Finterview with ITV News about the case
OL,10,Fthat nearly destroyed them too.
OL,12,FThey were threatened by the Post
OL,13,FOffice with legal action, in an effort
OL,14,Fto keep their discoveries quiet.
OL,16,F"A post office lawyer was upset with
OL,17,Fsomething I said in one of the working
OL,18,Fgroup meetings," remembered Mr
OL,19,FHenderson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
