OL,3,CThe private investigators who exposed
OL,4,CHorizon IT scandal
OL,6,F"He took me to one side and reminded
OL,7,Fme of my obligations under the non-
OL,8,Fdisclosure agreement.
OL,10,F"And basically, if I said anything out
OL,11,Fof line that could harm the Post
OL,12,FOffice, they would not hesitate to
OL,13,Ftake legal action against me. And he
OL,14,Fsaid, I would not be able to afford
OL,15,Ftheir legal fees. He was probably
OL,16,Fright."
OL,18,FBut Mr Henderson, a former soldier,
OL,19,Fwas not cowed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
