OL,6,FHe thought long and hard about
OL,7,Fquitting the investigation, only to be
OL,8,Ftalked out of it by Post Office
OL,9,Fcampaigners, who told him: "If you
OL,10,Fpull out there will be nothing between
OL,11,Fthe wolves and the post masters, so
OL,12,Fplease don't pull out", he recalled.
OL,14,FIn the end, the decision was made for
OL,15,Fthem and they were dismissed by the
OL,16,FPost Office.
