OL,6,FMore than a decade on, Paula Vennells
OL,7,F- the then-chief executive - began her
OL,8,Fevidence to the official inquiry with
OL,9,Fan apology to "Ron Warmington and Ian
OL,10,FHenderson for making their work
OL,11,Fharder."
OL,13,FThe men have waited a long time to
OL,14,Fdeliver their verdict on her.
OL,16,F"I'm certain that she knew," said Mr
OL,17,FWarmington, "but I think her brain
OL,18,Fseems to be working in a way that
OL,19,Fallows herself to know something, and
OL,20,Fthen to dismiss it from her mind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
