OL,6,FMr Henderson and Mr Warmington want a
OL,7,Fprompt police investigation to pick up
OL,8,Fwhere they left off all those years
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,FWhat is clear is that if the Post
OL,12,FOffice expected a whitewash from
OL,13,FSecond Sight, they picked the wrong
OL,14,Fguys.
OL,16,F"My parents ran a Post Office for many
OL,17,Fyears," Mr Henderson revealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
