OL,6,F"And very early on I realised we were
OL,7,Flooking at miscarriages of justice and
OL,8,Fmisconduct by senior people within the
OL,9,FPost Office and I wanted to expose
OL,10,Fthat."
OL,12,F"There was just so much that didn't
OL,13,Fmake sense. I mean why would hundreds
OL,14,Fof sub-postmasters go rogue and start
OL,15,Fstealing. It was implausible."
